00086 DataBlockWriter DoNothingReceiver::receive(
00087                 Integer fromModuleId, Integer service, Integer method, DataBlockReader args)
00088 {
00089         DataBlockWriter result ;
00090 
00091         switch (service)
00092         {
00093                 case SBWSystemService :
00094                         switch (method)
00095                         {
00096                                 case SBWGetMethodsMethod :
00097                                 case SBWGetServicesMethod :
00098                                         {
00099                                                 char *empty[] = {""} ;
00100                                                 result.add(0, empty);
00101 
00102                                                 return result ;
00103                                         }
00104                                 
00105                                 default :
00106                                         throw new SBWMethodNotFoundException("method doesn't exist");
00107                         }
00108 
00109                 default :
00110                         throw new SBWServiceNotFoundException("service doesn't exist");
00111         }
00112 }
